text: Stately mid-century 2 story home w/ Dutch hip roof on shy of 5 acres offers 2 homes, several barns & outbuildings & covered parking for 6+ vehicles. Main home has shy of 3000 sf, 3 BR's, 2 1/2 baths, newer addition of a family/library room on main floor & a sitting room upstairs off primary BR built in 1993. This lovely home offers 1 BR on the main floor and fashioned character in this home. Detached ADU (prev. antique & art gallery) has 1654 sf, 1 full bath, kitchen, stately fireplace, hook-ups for W/D, it's own 2 BR septic & private patio area. Both homes have brand new roof & gutters. Paved driveway & easy I-5 access.

Welcome Home in the Skagit Highlands Community. 3 bed, 2.5 baths tucked neatly on the court just steps from the local walking trail! With an open concept kitchen floor plan and stainless steel appliances & newer vinyl plank flooring this is the perfect starter home. Spacious master bedroom on upper level with a mountain view of Baker. Additional 2 bedrooms + neat bonus room great for office, art & more! Enjoy community living with parks, nature trails & easy access to the I-5 for convenient commuting north or south! Views of snow-capped mountains from your back yard with custom composite deck! 2 car garage & more this home will go fast!

Honey, pinch me!! I think I'm dreaming!! Well, Welcome to your Dream Home! This exquisite rambler, nestled on 2.81 acres of prime real estate, has breathtaking views of Big Lake. This luxurious property offers an unparalleled living experience, combining sophistication with comfort. The home boasts spacious bedrooms designed with comfort and elegance in mind. There is an office, a theater-game room for cinematic experiences, and a craft room to unleash your creativity and display your treasures.Year-round you can dive into the luxurious indoor pool that exudes a Mediterranean flair. Car enthusiasts will be delighted with the 12-car covered parking show garages, covered car wash, and driving the curvy country roads around Big Lake! Come see!

Wow! Location, location, location! Close to town, schools, play & more. This 3-bedroom home offers so much. Downstairs, enjoy a spacious, open kitchen with eat at counter and just off the french doors to back deck, great room joins the living and dining with fireplace and tons of natural light, plus a secondary dining/rec room around the corner, laundry, storage and 1/2 bath. Upstairs features the bedrooms, full bath, a family room with balcony and skylight and a large primary suite with vaulted ceilings, walk-in closet & en-suite bath. Backyard is fully fenced with a patio and front and back yards are a blank slate gardener's delight. 2-car garage off the alley. One owner, well-maintained. Bring your style and make this house your home!

If you've ever dreamed of living in a treehouse, here is the next best thing! A soaring, 16-foot ceiling opens up the great room of this Northwest contemporary-style home nestled in Shelter Bay. Stand-alone propane stove for warmth and ambience, seagrass laminate plank floors, and a custom-designed kitchen with light cherry-finished maple cabinets, amazing pantry storage, and more. Brand-new, 50-year roof and freshly-painted exterior. Two levels of decks for entertaining or birdwatching among the trees. A light-filled loft outside the upstairs primary bedroom would make a great exercise/artist studio or office. Enjoy privacy and seclusion along with easy access to all the amenities Shelter Bay has to offer!

Charming fixer-upper in Sedro-Woolley with incredible potential! Situated on a fully fenced, lovely spacious yard, the property offers plenty of room for outdoor activities & gardening. The large lot also presents the opportunity for future development of a duplex (Buyer to verify with city). The house itself needs some TLC, but with the right vision & effort, it could be transformed into a delightful home full of character. Additional features include a detached garage with work bench, storage and carport with convenient access to a pleasant alleyway. Being sold as-is, this is a perfect chance for an investor or homeowner looking to add their personal touch. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity!

Welcome to this charming home featuring 3 bedrooms + 1.75 baths w/ a fully-fenced detached ADU! Full of updates - brand new septic, 50-yr-roof recently installed, newer on demand hot water heater, new windows throughout, updated bath in ADU, and more - it's move-in ready and project free! The ADU is complete w/ 1 bed + .75 bath, living room, kitchen and separate parking. Two additional outbuildings (w/ power + heat) for whatever needs you may have. A large cement patio, private/fenced yard, ample driveway parking for RV's, boats and more! The location of this home can't be beat - easy access to I5, SR 20, HWY 9, and steps to the Skagit River! This home is great for anyone in need of an in-law suite, an income property, or investors!

Beautifully updated Burlington 3 bedroom rambler on large 10, 454 sf corner lot! This home has many upgrades for your enjoyment including laminate floors, recessed lighting, new wood stove insert , updated kitchen with SS appliances, French doors to covered patio, Air conditioning and more. Large bedrooms! Appliances including washer/dryer stay. Enjoy the huge back yard with covered patio for year round use. Large shed for additional storage and a small shed for lawn mower/yard tools. Garden space is ready for your plants. Large gate for RV/Car parking behind the fence next to the garage. Ready for you to move in and enjoy the Summer!

Embrace the charm of yesteryear in this 3-bed, 1-bath Victorian gem! Nestled just min from vibrant downtown Mount Vernon on a private 1/2 lot. Meander down the tree-lined driveway to privacy, surrounded by lush greenery. Enjoy serene evenings on the patio under a grape arbor trellis. Inside, find old-world charm melded seamlessly w/modern comforts. Warm yourself by the stone fp in the living rm, adorned w/beadboard walls & ceilings. HW floors lead to a beautifully updated kitchen, boasting an island, wood vent hood, & ample storage space. Fully fenced backyard. Huge mud/laundry rm & a unfinished bonus room the perfect hobby space. Oversized detached garage large enough to fit an RV or 4 cars. Welcome home to timeless elegance & tranquility.

This sweet rambler is waiting for you to call it home! It has 3 bedrooms, including a primary bedroom with continental bathroom access, full bathroom with new flooring and granite countertops. The Pullman style kitchen also has granite countertops and range/oven. Large window from the dining room looks over the fully fenced yard, perfect for firepit relaxing, lots of room for a garden or soccer games! The carport has an attached shed with storage area, covered area in back for toys or storage plus RV parking. This home awaits your finishing touches! Lots of potential here. This is an estate and is an as-is sale. Close to schools, shopping and historic downtown Mt Vernon. Newly shampooed carpet.

Welcome to Buchanan Hill, an impeccably maintained property set on a lush, landscaped lot of nearly an acre. This delightful home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 2, 118 square feet of spacious open concept living space, perfect for hosting gatherings. The well-appointed kitchen with ample counter space seamlessly connects to the large great room with a gas fireplace and views of Clear Lake. Outside, the manicured landscaping is equally impressive. A standout highlight is a detached garage spanning over 1500 square feet, complete with a wood stove and bathroom, providing ample storage and workspace. Whether you're a car enthusiast, hobbyist, or simply in need of extra room, this garage is a rare gem.

Calling all car buffs! 2983 sq ft, two-story w/ 4 car attached garage in the desirable Bayview neighborhood of Bridgewater Estates. Design an outdoor haven on the 1.2 acre nestled against a treed back drop providing room to breathe & more country setting to enjoy. Main floor Primary Bdrm w/sitting area, propane FP in Living room leading to deck offering hours of relaxation & is the perfect place to take in the Padilla Bay views. Large eat in kit w/newer appliances. Upstairs can accommodate work from home w/den/office loft, large family room w/balcony. 2 bdrms upstairs both w/ensuite baths, plus flex room & addtl full bath. New roof 2021, furnace in 2023. Create your ideal setting w/room to roam, ever-changing vistas plus Padilla Bay views.

Solid built one level home in a wonderful established location. This cute, 2 bedroom home & full bath has a cozy living room with a gas fireplace. RV parking, garage with stairs leading to a large attic with storage area. This is a perfect first home, considering downsizing or investment property as it's close to town, schools, parks and all city amenities.

Welcome to your charming retreat nestled in the heart of Sedro Woolley, WA. This home offers comfort, convenience, and modern touches. Inside there are two bedrooms and an open concept living room and kitchen. Outside there is a large yard to relax in and enjoy the NW summers. Located in the heart of Sedro Woolley, this home offers easy access to a wealth of amenities, including shopping, dining, parks, and more. Outdoor enthusiasts will appreciate the proximity to hiking trails, fishing spots, and other recreational activities, allowing you to embrace the vibrant lifestyle that the Pacific Northwest has to offer. Welcome to your Next Home.

This 4 bdrm, 1 bath 1596 sq. ft. built on 2 1/2 city lots, 2 story w/basement home, features a large 2 car detached garage w/attached workshop and an attic for storage , also a single car garage being used as a garden shed, and enjoy its magical garden spaces and sunny corner lot. This home, effectively built in 1915, boasts large rooms, with high ceilings and beautiful mahogany finishes. There is lots of storage Come see for yourself.

This exceptionally designed single level residence w/bonus room combines spacious, bright, open architecture with classic NW craftsman detailing. Living room features vaulted ceilings, cozy corner gas fireplace & flows into large dining area. Entertainment kitchen equipped with loads of storage, stainless, glistening granite countertops & oversized eating bar, perfect for gatherings. Expansive primary with ensuite bath provides high stature dual vanity, oversized walk-in shower, soaking tub & spacious walk-in closet. Two perfect guest bedrooms plus full guest bath. Outstanding upper level bonus area, perfect for office, theater room or play! Enjoy a wonderful extended covered back patio, easy care landscaping and a fantastic 3 car garage!

Grab the boat and ice chest, its Summertime on Big Lake! Welcome home to this adorable westerly facing lake front bungalow featuring 2 bedrooms, 1 bath and an extra finished area on the lower level adding additional sleeping area, sitting room and storage space. Enjoy the new entertainment sized deck, the front patio area and the large dock for all your water toys! The home has been updated throughout yet still offers the 1954 cabin feel. You will love the flow of the home and pass through kitchen bar area for that open concept feel. Walk to the Big Lake Bar & Grill, Outlook Golf Course is just around the corner, Walker Valley is minutes away, hiking trails everywhere and 15 minutes to I-5. Use as your primary, second home or AirBNB!

Ground Floor & End Unit with no steps required to access! This is one of the larger Units & it feels like it! 2 generous sized bedrooms & 2 full bathrooms. 2nd bedroom lives like a 2nd primary w/a in-room door to access the hall bath. Updated laminate flooring in living, dining & hallway. Double sliders lead out to huge patio. All appliances stay. One, close to unit, covered reserved parking space & one uncovered unassigned spot, one 8x5 on-floor storage unit. Two pets allowed for this unit, dogs/cats, no size limit. Condo dues cover water, sewer, garbage & common area maintenance. Intercom system to open the always locked lobby door for guests. Desirable central location near Skagit Valley College, Hospital, Shopping & Services!

Welcome back to the market! Don't miss a second chance at this rare opportunity. Remarkable 5-ac parcel offers breathtaking panoramic views of mountains & surrounding terrain w/ the ultimate privacy. Groundwork has been laid for you to build your dream home; private well & water system expertly installed w/ utility building & electricity on site. The land has been meticulously cleared & leveled providing the perfect blank canvas for your vision. Gain access to your private hilltop via long, scenic driveway. Situated in the highly sought-after Bow area, this property features rare combination of privacy & accessibility. Experience the magic of this exceptionally unique property for yourself! Scheduled visit w/ agents only pls.

Adorable updated home in the Hillcrest Park Community boasts this 3 bedroom, full bath home with a recently remodeled kitchen w/Granite countertops, double oven, gas cooktop & stainless appliances. A new tankless water heater, ductless heating & cooling system for increased comfort an energy efficiency. New LVP flooring & newer carpets in the bedrooms. New roof in 2023, new windows & hardie board siding in 2021. This is the perfect starter home w/extra storage in a lg. laundry room with new cabinets and quartz countertops. Enjoy the summers around the fire-pit area and a lg private, fenced back yard. A separate fenced area with a charming small chicken coop. Detached 400 s/f shop with a wood stove.

Experience modern living in this beautifully remodeled 1, 736 sq/ft home.Perfectly situated near the Skagit River, National Parks, &Sedro Wolley, this property offers an ideal blend of luxury & convenience.Step inside to find a brand-new kitchen equipped with quartz c-tops &new appliances, making meal prep a delight.The spacious layout includes a cozy bonus room featuring an inviting fireplace, perfect for relaxing evenings.Outside, enjoy a deck that provides stunning mountain views, ideal for entertaining or simply unwinding.Additional features include a detached 2car garage & ample parking space, ensuring all your storage & parking needs are met.Schedule a viewing today and embrace the perfect combination of contemporary style and natural beauty.

Beautifully redone Farm home on large flat, fully fenced lot. Lovely landscaped front yard. Nice large, spacious kitchen with hardwood laminate floors, gas stove. River rock gas fireplace off the dining area. Several skylights make the bonus room light and bright. Large french door leads to private, well landscaped backyard. Driveway parking, RV parking with plenty of off street parking. Large shed / shop. Close to shopping, easy access to downtown.

This is your chance to get a downtown condo in Anacortes that already has a license for short term and long term rentals. Unit B-1 is approximately 1, 240 sq. ft. with 2 bedrooms both with en-suite baths. Terrific location to take daily trips to San Juan Islands, whale watching, hiking trails, shops and restaurants.
nearby_schools: Anacortes School District, Northwest Educational Service District 189

text: Don't miss out on this lovely single-story home with views of the Skagit River. Conveniently situated on 8 acres, this charming residence offers 1, 680 square feet of living space, featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. The property also has a detached shop, perfect for additional storage or a workspace. The expansive yard provides endless opportunities for outdoor activities, gardening, or simply soaking in the tranquility of your private oasis. Conveniently located just minutes from local stores, gas stations, walking trails and a variety of recreational areas, this home perfectly balances peace and accessibility. Whether you're looking to explore the great outdoors or need quick access to daily necessities, this location offers it all.
